Ibaruwa yandikiwe mama

Mama yarangije gupakira imyenda ye mu gikapu gito.

Asohoka hanze, arampobera, arambwira ati: "Bye ubu."

"Mama, urajya he?" Namwitegereje ndamubaza.

Natangiye kurira nshaka kumukurikira ariko papa anzamura ku rutugu.

Papa ati: "Nyoko agiye mu bitaro kubyara."

Igihe numvise "mwana" naretse kurira ndamureba. "Kuki agiye gukura umwana mu bitaro?" Namubajije.

Papa yicaye ku ntebe nto arambwira ati: "Nzakubwira impamvu agiye gukura umwana mu bitaro."

Namuteze amatwi cyane nkuko yabisobanuye nubwo ntigeze numva neza impamvu atabyaye murugo. Papa arangije gusobanura, nabajije nti: "Azakomeza kunkunda nagaruka hamwe n'undi mwana?"

Data yaramfashe hafi arambwira ati: "Tuzahora tugukunda."

"Nshobora kumwandikira ibaruwa akiriho?" Nabajije papa.

Kuri uwo mugoroba, natangiye kwandikira mama ibaruwa.

Natanyuye impapuro mu gitabo cyanjye cy'imyitozo ngatangira kwandika ...

"Mama, mama, papa yavuze ko wagiye kuzana undi mwana ...

... Nyamuneka ihute usubire murugo ...

... Ndashaka ko uzana umwana wumukobwa, kugirango nshobore gukina nawe amaze gukura ...

... Urashobora kuzana bibiri kugirango umwe abe uwanjye ...

... Ndagutegereje hano hanze y'inzu yacu. "

Nafunze ibaruwa yanjye kugira ngo nshobore kuyiha data kugira ngo nzane mama. Nkibyuka bukeye bwaho, ibaruwa yari yagiye.
